    "deployed": false,
    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces BSA's open case data (applications, resolutions, the legacy calendar index, pre-application meetings), publishes the hearing calendar that has no dataset today, and adds file_variance_application \u2014 the net-new write workflow that today is a paper PDF-form intake with no online portal.",
